Send challenges to friends using points
10+ challenge categories
AI verification of completion proof
Reward/penalty system (1,000-8,000 points)
üí∞ Points Economy
Earn: Likes (+50), Comments (+120), Challenges (+3,000)
Spend: Posts (-150), Calls (-100/min), Challenges (-2,000)
Purchase: RM5 (5,000 pts) to RM100 (220,000 pts)
üéÆ Challenge Categories
Social Challenges - Get strangers to sign up, compliment people
Entertainment - Karaoke performances, dance teaching
Community Service - Help elderly, clean public spaces
Acts of Kindness - Buy drinks for strangers, volunteer work
Cultural - Speak only Bahasa Malaysia, cultural activities
Fitness - Running goals, sports challenges
Business - Networking events, skill development
üèÜ Success Metrics
Target Engagement:
Daily Active Users: 70%+
